3/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ab9e1c36-a530-493d-95e2-edb4e4033717.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ab9e1c36-a530-493d-95e2-edb4e4033717.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"1. Affordable Skin Transformation"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p>Who says youthful, radiant skin has to come from pricey treatments? The <strong>Salmon PDRN Collagen Mask</strong> helps <strong>repair, firm, and brighten</strong> your skin from within — boosting collagen, refining pores, and restoring that healthy glow. Get visible results that feel luxurious, <strong>without the luxury price tag.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/For_LP_6.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","label":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","default":"2. Scientifically Proven Ingredients"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxwUzin72S_text","label":"ggxwUzin72S_text","default":"<p>Our mask harnesses the power of <strong>Salmon DNA (PDRN)</strong>—rich in polynucleotides—to <strong>stimulate skin cell regeneration</strong>. This renewal process helps <strong>enhance elasticity</strong>, <strong>reduce the look of fine lines</strong>, and <strong>restore a youthful, radiant appearance</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>PDRN</strong>, derived from Salmon DNA, is renowned for its <strong>regenerative</strong> and <strong>repairing</strong> properties. Studies associate it with improved <strong>skin texture and tone</strong>, making it a trusted active in <strong>advanced, results-driven skincare</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9IIKcaXL6_label","label":"gg9IIKcaXL6_label","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:13px;\"><strong>Check availability</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/Bonnie1_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/Untitled_design_2_f8c47b58-64be-4162-b91b-ab9765cde65b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/Bonnie1_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","label":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","default":"3. <strong>Deep Hydration - Salmon DNA</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","label":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","default":"<p>Infused with <strong>Salmon PDRN (polynucleotides)</strong>, this advanced formula goes beyond surface moisture to <strong>revitalize skin from within</strong>. The bioactive molecules help <strong>restore hydration balance</strong>, strengthen the skin barrier, and improve elasticity for a smoother, plumper look. Unlike ordinary masks, it locks in moisture at the cellular level — leaving your skin <strong>deeply hydrated, supple, and glowing</strong> long after you remove it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/e1ec189dba6bd9c29cee8063aff551d1.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/e1ec189dba6bd9c29cee8063aff551d1.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/e1ec189dba6bd9c29cee8063aff551d1.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","label":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","default":"4. Sensitive Skin Friendly"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","label":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","default":"<p>If you have sensitive skin like me, finding something gentle yet truly effective can be tough. That’s why I love this mask — it’s powered by <strong>Salmon PDRN</strong>, known for its ability to <strong>repair and strengthen</strong> the skin barrier while keeping it calm and hydrated. It helps <strong>soothe irritation</strong>, <strong>boost collagen</strong>, and <strong>restore elasticity</strong>, giving even the most delicate skin a <strong>smooth, radiant glow</strong> without any redness or discomfort. It’s the kind of gentle care that actually transforms your skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-46ddba81-6c7e-441b-b2d1-edeebc781354.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHIzq54zz__text","label"